            "title": "\"Pokimane\" on Scaling a Streaming Business",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"k1rG6TQsjThCWxE06Q0\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content='\"Pokimane\" on Scaling a Streaming Business' itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content='Hollywood is typically focused on the people in front of the camera - and, increasingly, that means streamers like Imane Anys, aka \"Pokimane,\" one of the most popular streamers on Twitch with nearly 10 million dedicated followers. She joins Caroline Hyde and Ed Ludlow on \"Bloomberg Tech.\"\n' itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-10-09T23:18:47+02:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3473913.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=k1rG6TQsjThCWxE06Q0\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               Hollywood is typically focused on the people in front of the camera - and, increasingly, that means streamers like Imane Anys, aka \"Pokimane,\" one of the most popular streamers on Twitch with nearly 10 million dedicated followers. She joins Caroline Hyde and Ed Ludlow on \"Bloomberg Tech.\"<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51303616');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
