            "title": "Seeing Early Signs of Silver Outperforming Gold: Citi's Layton",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"k69Ony3EHdtcv4E06JC\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content=\"Seeing Early Signs of Silver Outperforming Gold: Citi's Layton\" itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content='Spot silver prices jumped to the highest level in decades as surging demand for safe-haven assets ran into supply constraints in the London bullion market. Silver has been boosted this year by the so-called \"debasement trade,\" with investors flocking to the perceived safety of Bitcoin, gold and silver. Gold also hit a record this week as it passed $4,000 at one point. On \"Bloomberg Markets,\" Scarlet Fu talks with Max Layton, global head of commodities research at Citi (C), about the surge in prices and his price targets.\n' itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-10-09T23:07:06+02:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3473912.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=k69Ony3EHdtcv4E06JC\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               Spot silver prices jumped to the highest level in decades as surging demand for safe-haven assets ran into supply constraints in the London bullion market. Silver has been boosted this year by the so-called \"debasement trade,\" with investors flocking to the perceived safety of Bitcoin, gold and silver. Gold also hit a record this week as it passed $4,000 at one point. On \"Bloomberg Markets,\" Scarlet Fu talks with Max Layton, global head of commodities research at Citi (C), about the surge in prices and his price targets.<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51303534');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
